OL,6,FExecutive ministers have agreed to
OL,7,Fincrease the regional element of rates
OL,8,Fbills in Northern Ireland in line with
OL,9,Finflation.
OL,11,FFinance Minister Caoimhe Archibald had
OL,12,Fproposed a 4% rise at the meeting of
OL,13,Fthe devolved administration at
OL,14,FStormont Castle on Thursday.
