OL,6,FThe Executive's move, which is subject
OL,7,Fto the approval of the Assembly, comes
OL,8,Famid a demand from the UK Government
OL,9,Ffor the devolved administration to
OL,10,Fraise an additional #113 million of
OL,11,Fits own revenues in the coming
OL,12,Ffinancial year.
OL,14,FA 4% increase in the regional rate
OL,15,Fwould equate to around #30 million
OL,16,Fextra in revenue.
