OL,6,FMs Archibald was accompanied by First
OL,7,FMinister Michelle O'Neill and deputy
OL,8,FFirst Minister Emma Little-Pengelly as
OL,9,Fthey announced the decision to
OL,10,Freporters outside Stormont Castle
OL,11,Fafter the meeting.
OL,13,FFirst Minister Michelle O'Neill said
OL,14,Frates bills would go out to
OL,15,Fhouseholders as scheduled in April.
