OL,6,F"We're very mindful of the pressures
OL,7,Fthat all households are feeling right
OL,8,Fnow and particularly businesses as
OL,9,Fwell and we have therefore decided to
OL,10,Fkeep the regional rates in line with
OL,11,Finflation," she said.
OL,13,FMs O'Neill added: "The Executive has
OL,14,Falways been very clear that we're up
OL,15,Ffor the challenge of transforming our
OL,16,Fpublic services but we only can
OL,17,Fachieve that if the long term
OL,18,Ffinancial package is in place and the
OL,19,Fright long term financial package is
OL,20,Fin place.
