OL,6,F"So the Finance Minister has continued
OL,7,Fto have very constructive
OL,8,Fconversations with the Treasury and we
OL,9,Fintend to continue that engagement."
OL,11,FDeputy First Minister Emma Little-
OL,12,FPengelly said engagement with the
OL,13,FTreasury to secure more financial
OL,14,Fsupport for the Stormont Executive has
OL,15,Fbeen "positive" so far.
OL,17,F"We know that there are a huge number
OL,18,Fof families in Northern Ireland that
OL,19,Fare under significant financial
OL,20,Fpressure," she said.
