OL,6,F"For businesses with a rateable value
OL,7,Fof #50,000 it will mean an additional
OL,8,F#10.73 per week. I want to reassure
OL,9,Fhouseholds and businesses that the
OL,10,Fexisting #350 million of rates support
OL,11,Fthat is in place will still be there
OL,12,Fto help them in the year ahead.
OL,14,F"And I think it's important to say
OL,15,Fthat negotiations continue. The step
OL,16,Fthat we have taken today is because
OL,17,Fthose engagements with Treasury and
OL,18,Fthe UK government have been positive.
OL,19,FWe're hopeful in terms of the days and
OL,20,Fweeks ahead to get further clarity in
OL,21,Frelation to some of those aspects.
OL,26,@nD@AOUvD@AOU
