OL,6,F"So this is very much a decision taken
OL,7,Fin the context of those negotiations
OL,8,Fthat have taken place and the nature
OL,9,Fand the positive nature of those
OL,10,Fnegotiations thus far."
OL,12,FStormont Finance Minister Caoimhe
OL,13,FArchibald described her talks with the
OL,14,FTreasury on Wednesday as
OL,15,F"constructive".
