OL,6,F"We all want the best public services
OL,7,Fand when you listen to ministers
OL,8,Faround the Executive table, the
OL,9,Fcurrent projections indicate an
OL,10,Fextremely difficult financial
OL,11,Fposition," she said.
OL,13,F"I had a constructive first meeting
OL,14,Fwith the Treasury yesterday and look
OL,15,Fforward to continued engagement in the
OL,16,Ftime ahead on a number of matters,
OL,17,Fincluding a new fiscal framework."
